Element


keycode
&keycode.purpose;


&keycode.synopsis.gen;
Description



The KeyCode identifies the numeric value associated with
a key on a computer keyboard. This is distinct from any scan code
that it may generate (KeyCode), or any symbolic name
(KeySym) that might exist for the key.


